L LAZEENA SABA-QOONAA BIL-IMAANE WA LAA TAJ-A’L FEE QOLOO-BENAA GHILLAN LIL-LAZEENA AA-MANOO. RABBANAA RAOO-FUR RAHEE-MOON SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HI WAS-TUR A’LAIYYA ZONOO-BEE WA O’YOO-BEE WAGH-FIR LEE BE-HAQQE MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN INNA-KAR RAOO-FUR RAHEEMO.", "ArabicText1": "رَبَّنَا هَبْ لَنَا مِنْ اَزْوَاجِنَا وَذُرِّيَّاتِنَا قُرَّةَ اَعْيُنٍ وَاجْعَلْنَا لِلْمُتَّقِيْنَ اِمَامًا۔ رَبَّنَا عَلَيْكَ تَوَكَّلْنَا وَاِلَيْكَ اَنَبْنَا وَاِلَيْكَ الْمَصِيْرُ۔ رَبَّنَا لَا تَجْعَلْنَا فِتْنَةً لِلَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْا رَبَّنَا اغْفِرْ لَنَا ذُنُوبَنَا وَلِاِخْوَانِنَا الَّذِيْنَ سَبَقُوْنَا بِالْاِيْمَانِ وَلَا تَجْعَلْ فِيْ قُلُوْبِنَا غِلًّا لِلَّذِيْنَ آمَنُوْا۔ رَبَّنَا اِنَّكَ رَؤُفٌ رَّحِيْمٌ‌ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ وَاسْتُرْ عَلَيَّ ذُنُوْبِيْ وَعُيُوْبِيْ وَاغْفِرْ لِيْ بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ اِنَّكَ الرَّءُوْفُ الرَّحِيْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "Ar